{"tid":1073953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敵對YouTuber號召打人　逾400粉絲現真身互毆","createTime":"2019-03-23T05:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T23:26:50.000Z","uid":176442,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"84a7a14182fd90088d1e23d12a9ab650c91803ee","tid":1073953,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190323/bkn-20190323120016889-0323_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190323%2Fbkn-20190323120016889-0323_00912_001.html&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=02d2651b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190323/bkn-20190323120016889-0323_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"45505cdcc54bf30c064dc6ebd6097a2f1e934092","tid":1073953,"uid":176442,"like":253,"dislike":1,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"德國有2名積怨甚深的網紅YouTuber，近日竟各自呼籲自己的支持者，於周四（21日）前往首都柏林的亞歷山大廣場，與對方的「粉絲」一較高下。逾400名網民放下鍵盤趕赴現場，結果有近半百人毆成一團，有人甚至出動利刃以及投擲石塊。警方派出逾百警力趕赴現場，行動中拘捕9人。 <br />\n<br />\n網紅「Thatsbekir」和「Bahar Al Amood」在網上不時發生「口水戰」，詎料演變成現實混戰。兩人的支持者於當日傍晚在廣場對峙，初時只是少許肢體碰撞，其後約有50人開始動手動腳，最後更打成一團。 <br />\n<br />\n大量警員接報後趕到現場，出動胡椒噴霧以及施放催淚氣體，以驅散人群。當地傳媒報道，事故中有2名警員及6人受傷。警察工會主席基奧馬（Norbert Cioma）呼籲，有大量支持者的網紅理應更有責任感；他感嘆道：「網紅有時低估了自己影響力。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365ffa48200d2541333cd274873f4ecde7e3580c","tid":1073953,"uid":58335,"like":354,"dislike":8,"score":346,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"精人出口，笨人出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68344c43d154d7e589ec582c01c26a5abb491796","tid":1073953,"uid":22574,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T05:15:13.000Z","msg":"幾時到個香港痴線聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c756665d4d0d5a0980730a3876ac98d3771a00f4","